{"tid":1746620,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[港豬］話說去咗蘭桂坊","createTime":"2019-11-22T22:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T22:42:42.000Z","uid":16250,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a60c051fdf060c4e2180d1b3c670ca49383f8607","tid":1746620,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:27:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n有個中學朋友突然問我去唔去飲杯嘢<br />\n我就問佢去邊呀 佢話：「老蘭 有枱喎」<br />\n我當堂吓一跳 然後得啖笑<br />\n雖則幾年前曾經同佢差唔多個個禮拜落去<br />\n但係我都即刻話：「唔去喇 好攰」咁樣<br />\n跟着佢話佢生日<br />\n啊... 原來冇用facebook之後真係會唔知曾經成日一齊玩嘅朋友幾時生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就話：「咁好啦 」就決定咗去吓啦 街坊裝出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到嘅時候 個世界同我諗嘅完全兩回事<br />\n我喺度諗我究竟係咪仲喺香港呢<br />\n個人好似入咗平行時空咁 <br />\nD鬼佬呀 mk妹呀 mk仔呀 原來同以前一樣冇變 <br />\n釣狗公嘅就繼續釣 狗公嘅就繼續狗<br />\n<br />\n我問我朋友：「呢排應該少咗人去浦？ 」<br />\n佢話：「少咗但都係咁 」（我見其實唔算少⋯）<br />\n佢話佢都係個個星期去<br />\n我問佢萬聖節有冇出呀？ <br />\n佢話有不過今年萬聖節變咗11月1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話我10月31有出嚟呀 發夢呀 佢就哈哈兩聲就冇繼續講呢個話題<br />\n<br />\n到最後我話前兩日衰咗呀 好彩最後冇事 佢好似冇乜特別反應<br />\n我講笑話差啲就要10年後先慶祝你生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我覺得掃咗佢興<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以決定早走 <br />\n二來因為成個環境都好格格不入 同唔到嗰啲人soso<br />\n仲有條友話：「咦！你好少出嚟蒲？」<br />\n我話：「好耐冇咯...」<br />\n佢話咩：「我都係呀 而家去大陸玩」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽到呢度已經冇理佢之後講佢d夜浦功略⋯<br />\n不過都係因為我毒撚性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其實我想講 原來真係有班人 到而家都係馬照跑舞照跳 好似幾個月乜事都冇發生過咁<br />\n<br />\n不過我冇後悔出嚟抗爭 咁投入呢場運動<br />\n我覺得自己只要堅持信念 <br />\n你班港豬明又好唔明又好<br />\n關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噏風發完<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經嘢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家記得去投個票！<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"6266811ce112f3d89476fd5b1ab0e4334ad73c2f","tid":1746620,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:31:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nVt5tC9ZKJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnVt5tC9ZKJM&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgmqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a3d473ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nVt5tC9ZKJM</a>"},{"pid":"447db0a2bab77fdb08d465db9cebe0c13ecafc33","tid":1746620,"uid":321867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:33:58.000Z","msg":"隔住個mon都feel到尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81857722ae8172e97b1d5bf7951e816c0ba9e3b2","tid":1746620,"uid":206375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入去燒錢 自己圍內fd飲算啦"},{"pid":"49650af999f597f0babb557b6eace5cf97d8bb4f","tid":1746620,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81857722ae8172e97b1d5bf7951e816c0ba9e3b2","tid":1746620,"uid":206375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入去燒錢 自己圍內fd飲算啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"咁又唔使俾錢嘅<br />\n爛船仲有三根釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed74990e1a7c5da11fdde56707b43f02e59c867","tid":1746620,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"447db0a2bab77fdb08d465db9cebe0c13ecafc33","tid":1746620,"uid":321867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:33:58.000Z","msg":"隔住個mon都feel到尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so